college: College of Law, Governance and Policy
blurb: To enrol in this course you must be studying a: Juris Doctor (MJD) and have completed or be completing five 1000 or 6100 level LAWS courses. You are not able to apply for this clinic if you have previously completed a LAWS coded clinical course. Students can only complete one clinical course during their degree. You will need to formally apply to enrol into this course. Please contact the ANU College of Law, Governance and Policy for more information.
